= TTF_GetFreeTypeVersion =

This function stores the version of the FreeType2 library in use.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
void TTF_GetFreeTypeVersion(int *major, int *minor, int *patch);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''major'''
|pointer to get the major version number
|-
|'''minor'''
|pointer to get the minor version number
|-
|'''patch'''
|pointer to get the param version number
|}

== Remarks ==

[[TTF_Init]]() should be called before calling this function.

